Author: Luke1
Title: 🔥🔥[ANN][LYFE - Wellness Rewards and Gamification]🔥🔥
Body: https://medium.com/@lyfehealth/lyfex-your-stable-token-50d849108967  Greetings Lyfe Buddy!  As a development of the Lyfe Wallet feature, we present LyfeX on our Lyfe app. You may already know, Lyfe Tokens are not only able to be exchanged for various vouchers and promos, but also a LYFE cryptocurrency that can be traded digitally.  LyfeX is present to you as a stable token to complete the market-based Lyfe Token ecosystem. To know about LyfeX further, you can look to these 4 points:  Stable-token LyfeX is a token that backed-up by asset. Via Lyfe app, you can exchange Lyfe Tokens to various LyfeX tokens, which will be backed-up with various physical assets. For a start, Lyfe will presents LyfeXGold or LyfeG as the first product.  Each LyfeG token will be based on physical gold assets in the Lyfe custodian partner. Lyfe tokens can be exchanged to LyfeG via Lyfe app, according to the physical gold price currently applied.  One thing you need to keep in mind: this exchange can only apply in one direction, that is, from Lyfe Token to LyfeX.  2. Asset-based  The LyfeX Token you have can be exchanged into a real physical asset. Like LyfeG for example, you can exchange it into physical gold. This exchange can be done only at our Lyfe custodian partner. Terms and conditions applied.  3. Custodian  Exchange of LyfeX tokens into physical assets can only be done at Lyfe custodian partners. This Lyfe and custodians partnership is meant to audit and custody your assets.  4. Asset Transfer  You can send LyfeX tokens as digital assets to other Lyfe app users, in any location. The recipient can also exchange LyfeX tokens into physical assets in Lyfe custodian partners that are available in their location, terms and conditions applied.  The Lyfe app and its various interesting features will be coming soon to your smartphone. Always stay tune on our Telegram channel, Medium, and social media accounts to be the first to know the latest info from Lyfe.

Author: boltz
Title: 🔥🔥[ANN][LYFE - Wellness Rewards and Gamification]🔥🔥
Body: The Lyfe Token is a utility token built with smart contracts that is the core of the Lyfe Platform.  Its purpose is to enable the pursuit of better well-being through rewards and redemption.     LyfeREWARDS   Blockchain Rewards and Loyalty. LyfeREWARDS is a decentralised rewards program to incentivise people to live a healthy lifestyle. LyfeREWARDS will distribute Lyfe Tokens to users who are eligible and have completed the challenge. Lyfe Rewards will measure and distribute the rewards according to data point received from the various fitness and health apps or wearable devices that are onboard of Lyfe platform.     Rewarding Everyone   Benefits for Community and Users  ⦁ Get rewarded with tokens while living a healthy lifestyle. ⦁ Chances to win it big and gain millions of token by participating in various virtual Lyfe Challenge ⦁ More accurate fitness data interpretation and key health guidance with cross-platform data analysis      Benefits for Health Tech Developer  ⦁ Incentivise and monetise directly with endless possibilites for collaboration ⦁ Cross-platform SDK with integrated Wallet and Exchange System ⦁ More efficient user acquisition with huge pool of users shared across platform      Benefits for Healthcare Company and Establishments  ⦁ Effective promotion with accurate targeting of users down to their behavior. ⦁ Acquire more accurate, targeted data from various data points for research purpose ⦁ Opportunity to gain additional revenue by onboarding eligibile service   Be Healthy, Make Money  Nowadays, health is no longer a top priority for many people. In this fast-paced world, our lives are getting so busy to the point where we only start thinking about our health when it is too late. Wouldn't it be great if we can maintain a healthy lifestyle while getting paid at the same time? With Lyfe, you can do exactly that. Lyfe is a wellness rewards and gamification platform that will incentivise users to live a healthier life  More than half of people abandon their health devices and apps due to lack of engagement and incentives. With Open API and SDK, Lyfe will allow app developers to integrate the Lyfe Challenge and Rewards platform into their own ecosystem, taking advantage of the value and exchangeability factor of the Lyfe token.  Benefits for Users  ⦁   Get rewarded with tokens while living a healthy lifestyle. ⦁   More accurate fitness data interpretation and key health guidance with cross-platform data analysis  Benefits for Partners  ⦁   Incentivize and monetise directly, with endless possibilites for collaboration ⦁   More efficient user acquisition through our large pool of users shared across platforms ⦁   Acquire more accurate, targeted data from various data points for research and promotion      LyfeCHALLENGE  We will work with our various partners in the wellness industry to create Lyfe Challenges that users can complete to earn Lyfe Tokens. This includes things from basic physical exercise, to medical challenges such as maintaining blood glucose level and blood pressure. With our open-access API and cross-platform SDK, users can use their current wearables/fitness watches to easily track their activity.  Additionally, community and multiplayer challenges allow fun interaction between the users, and will motivate users to do their best. Friendly competition will make it easier to develop healthy habits, not to mention more fun and exciting!
